But you define true perseverance and persistence.

286
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:00,240
You are the pride of our class.

287
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:03,760
That's all for the second year of high school. The manuscript of Panlin Road.

288
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:14,480
School doctor.

289
